		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So, lets say I hack a Darkwing Duck cart. Its MMC1 and it has two 27C010 EEPROMS, one for the PRG and another for the CHR. Do I need any extra hacking in the cartdridge?. Or just by changing the old EEPROMS by my 29F040 all will work fine?. I have also a MMC1 Kid Icarus cart that has 128kb of PRG and uses CHR RAM. And for MMC3 I have a Rockman 4 with 512kb of PRG and CHR RAM. So, If I understood it well, I'll had to hack one cartdridge for games with PRG and CHR ROMS, and another for games that uses CHR RAM, right?.
<br />Thanks a lot for the quick repply <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" />:
